              Our 3-piece tan brown floral print crepe suit set features a straight-fit kurta with a notched neckline, three-quarter sleeves, and a statement yoke. Complemented with straight trouser pants with a partially elasticated waistband and roomy pockets, and a matching dupatta. This elegant style is perfect for light festivities

              Accessorise with jhumka earrings, a fold-over clutch bag, and slip-on heels to complete the look.

              The model (height 170 cm) is wearing a size S.
